    desc: "You receive a firm, written quote before any work starts. No surprise add-ons. No hidden fees. Ever. You approve it first.",
  },
  {
    step: "04",
    title: "Guaranteed Fix",
    desc: "We complete the repair using OEM-quality parts and back every job with our 90-day parts and labor warranty.",
